hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46a303c66bf725ad8d753460dd0d35ac4e9ed27","tid":763063,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"報咩cic<br />\n係就做下學師試水溫先<br />\n做完覺得頂到先搵你老細簽中工比你都唔遲<br />\n<br />\n你讀完個所謂課程之後入行<br />\n其實同wiki完&ldquo;電腦&rdquo;之後就入行做it狗冇分別<br />\n<br />\n而且我當你唔聽勸，堅持要讀<br />\n讀完都唔好行出嚟同人講自己中工<br />\n頂住個名不副實嘅頭銜唔比人玩死都笑死<br />\n<br />\n另外，讀唔讀都好<br />\n入左行比人屌就梗架啦，對比人屌有太大抗拒嘅人唔適合做地盤"},{"pid":"d8cb1bc2c159a2cbe1b3e04e70eefc0c29faeeb4","tid":763063,"uid":143190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:42:43.000Z","msg":"18就做緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b54feaeec9fd5e55a9f1942a96372c9348690a","tid":763063,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8cb1bc2c159a2cbe1b3e04e70eefc0c29faeeb4","tid":763063,"uid":143190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:42:43.000Z","msg":"18就做緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:50:58.000Z","msg":"我都係咁上下歲數開始做<br />\n啲師博直頭唔係叫我後生仔，係叫小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5bb6803535cc1dbaf5743ae12c826ffebc77317","tid":763063,"uid":143190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56b54feaeec9fd5e55a9f1942a96372c9348690a","tid":763063,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8cb1bc2c159a2cbe1b3e04e70eefc0c29faeeb4","tid":763063,"uid":143190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:42:43.000Z","msg":"18就做緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:50:58.000Z","msg":"我都係咁上下歲數開始做<br />\n啲師博直頭唔係叫我後生仔，係叫小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk